Note:
RUNA Traceback Library: Real-time Monitoring and Streaming Analytics Module

Revolutionary real-time monitoring system that provides continuous streaming analytics
for production systems. Combines stack trace analysis, performance correlation, and
temporal debugging with live monitoring capabilities for comprehensive production
observability and automated incident response.

Key Features:
- Real-time stack trace streaming and aggregation across distributed systems
- Live performance correlation analysis with adaptive thresholds
- Automated anomaly detection with machine learning-like pattern recognition
- Production-safe monitoring with minimal overhead and circuit breakers
- Multi-dimensional metrics streaming with configurable retention policies
- Alert correlation and incident response automation
- Distributed system health monitoring with service dependency mapping
- Custom metric definition and streaming with flexible aggregation windows
- Integration with external monitoring systems and alerting platforms
- Historical trend analysis with predictive capacity planning
- Dynamic threshold adjustment based on system behavior patterns
- Comprehensive dashboards and visualization capabilities for operations teams
:End Note

Import module "traceback/traceback" as Traceback
Import module "traceback/temporal" as Temporal
Import module "traceback/correlation" as Correlation
Import module "time/core" as TimeCore
Import module "time/network" as NetworkTime
Import module "collections" as Collections

Note: Real-time Monitoring Types and Stream Processing Framework
Type called "MonitoringSession":
            session_id as String
            monitoring_config as MonitoringConfig
            stream_processors as List[StreamProcessor]
            metric_collectors as List[MetricCollector]
            alert_managers as List[AlertManager]
            dashboard_services as List[DashboardService]
            correlation_session as Correlation.PerformanceCorrelationSession
            temporal_session as Temporal.TemporalDebugSession
            session_statistics as MonitoringStatistics
            is_active as Boolean
            metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type called "MonitoringConfig":
            sampling_rate_percent as Float
            max_overhead_percent as Float
            enable_circuit_breakers as Boolean
            stream_buffer_size as Integer
            metric_retention_hours as Integer
            alert_correlation_window_ms as Integer
            enable_predictive_analysis as Boolean
            dashboard_refresh_interval_ms as Integer
            distributed_coordination as Boolean
            external_integrations as List[ExternalIntegration]
            metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type called "StreamProcessor":
            processor_id as String
            processor_type as ProcessorType
            input_streams as List[String]
            output_streams as List[String]
            processing_config as ProcessingConfig
            aggregation_windows as List[AggregationWindow]
            filter_conditions as List[FilterCondition]
            transformation_rules as List[TransformationRule]
            throughput_metrics as ThroughputMetrics
            is_active as Boolean
            metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type ProcessorType is:
            | Aggregator
            | Filter
            | Transformer
            | Correlator
            | Alerter
            | Enricher

Type called "ProcessingConfig":
            batch_size as Integer
            processing_timeout_ms as Integer
            max_memory_usage_mb as Integer
            parallelism_level as Integer
            backpressure_strategy as BackpressureStrategy
            error_handling_strategy as ErrorHandlingStrategy
            checkpointing_enabled as Boolean
            metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type BackpressureStrategy is:
            | Drop
            | Buffer
            | Block
            | Sample

Type ErrorHandlingStrategy is:
            | Skip
            | Retry
            | DeadLetter
            | Fail

Type called "AggregationWindow":
            window_id as String
            window_type as WindowType
            duration_ms as Integer
            slide_interval_ms as Integer
            aggregation_functions as List[AggregationFunction]
            grouping_keys as List[String]
            output_stream as String
            metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type WindowType is:
            | Tumbling
            | Sliding
            | Session

Type AggregationFunction is:
            | Count
            | Sum
            | Average
            | Min
            | Max
            | Percentile
            | StandardDeviation

Type called "MetricCollector":
            collector_id as String
            metric_type as MetricType
            collection_interval_ms as Integer
            target_components as List[String]
            metric_dimensions as List[String]
            collection_strategy as CollectionStrategy
            data_quality_checks as List[QualityCheck]
            streaming_destination as String
            collector_health as CollectorHealth
            metadata as Dictionary[String, Any]

Type MetricType is:
